On the night of the 25th, the "Omachi Taromen Management Council" (represented by Kensuke Suzuyama), which is made up of stores that serve Omachi Town's famous noodle "Taromen", served "Taromen" at the town general welfare center Misato, which serves as an evacuation center for victims of torrential rains.
